Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這簡直像是復活了啊  -啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了 面碼居然為了讓你幫她實現願望回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...我覺得這只是我看到的幻想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.16,0:02:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想?也就是Fantasy?太帥了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 她現在在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...現在沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.04,0:02:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡 面碼 快出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心把面碼的事說出來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:22.66,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他居然直接相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.12,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了這只是我自己的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太就是厲害啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 那個 這個秘密基地是你在用的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只是在日本的時候用下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那些紅色的 是我去過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到世界各地去看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以攢下打工賺的錢去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那破玩意 哪有時間去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間我還去東南亞轉了圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越南的女孩子好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時明明是個小豆丁來著 居然就長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:15.58,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣 這樣 這樣的 好可愛啊 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是變了不少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-JungleCruise 會出來什麼呢  -不用脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 跑題了 跑題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說面碼的願望啊 你們曾經約定過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 我也不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是說過想要仁太的「的呦」的簽名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.28,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(「的呦」搞笑藝人)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個會專門化成鬼魂出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-會不會是那個呢  -嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 栗丸你怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回家給你喝優酪乳哦 優酪乳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 鳴子 你真的去了嗎 宿海家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要去找那個家裡蹲你真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 其實挺正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.43,0:04:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎麼的就是提不起幹勁 早上起不來床之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也會...經常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不過我可不想被拿來和那種陰沉的傢伙相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他一定在想關於鳴子的H的事 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 很可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王大附高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膩味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴...鶴見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊 你丟東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況你就放著別管就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被別人看見我和綠高的學生說話就丟死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還特意拿給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:58.46,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行不行 anaru和鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候變得這麼臭屁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.20,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前總是羞怯怯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前起就容易受別人影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在和跟你在一起的那些股間很不矜持的女人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,股間?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明總是在模仿本間芽衣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨隨便便說出死人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己說出來倒搞得自己最難受 真是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 雪集也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想變得...像面碼一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 仁太啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是喜歡面碼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有說那種話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰 誰會喜歡這種醜女...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後...就出了那種事...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙一叫起來 就~回家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:06.96,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(青蛙和回家讀音一樣)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙一叫起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼 究竟應該回哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?口袋妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人買什麼你還有意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口袋妖怪的哪版啊 蛋白石 還是祖母綠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?口袋妖怪 金?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪個年代的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 要是有的話就賣給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 趕緊拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?稀有口袋妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 面碼不是很想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一直都沒弄到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 她還說過大金剛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四千五百七十一元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前出的遊戲居然按定價賣 太黑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可告訴你 這已經是很有良心的價格了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經很難入手了 已經升值了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thankyou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 歡迎回來 仁太君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天現場出了個很棒的盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯我們吃烤肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我現在沒食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?什麼嘛 真不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼弄來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...最開始先從三隻裡面選一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力具現化成的我的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就應該是不存在的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啊 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:18.02,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(勇者面碼 找到了口袋妖怪商店)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波...久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還像以前那樣叫我波波嘛 那麼見外幹什麼 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次有人這樣叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 對了雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 面碼在仁太那裡復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 事到如今還...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:11:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海怎麼說面碼的?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 好久沒見仁太了 那傢伙還是那麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海是怎麼說面碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...幻聽?還是幻想來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記不大清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼好像請他幫忙實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好 秒睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~仁太~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼洗澡了啊 老爸還沒出門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 仁太 一洗澡就冷颼颼地 面碼最討厭這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 稍微注意一下自己的發育狀況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 某部分似乎沒有什麼成長...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某部分?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先把衣服穿上!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?怎麼是個有點面熟的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 莫非是波波君?好大個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.17,DefaultA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發育期真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與朋友交換?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 據說用聯機線交換怪獸的話就能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 叔叔 肉很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天晚上剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔去上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您走好~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我完全都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 面碼也說不是大家在一起就實現不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊波波 你怎麼想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是雪...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 我也看到幻聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻聽可是看不到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.70,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是這樣啊 只要能再找到一個口袋妖怪的卡帶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找個人和我交換...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候最討厭自己捲曲的前發和眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對直發的面碼...受到仁太偏愛的面碼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru 我們貼一樣的貼紙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 這個很可愛吧 也給anaru一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最喜歡面碼 卻又最討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子!有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太會使喚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦!anaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 我也要玩口袋妖怪?難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾玩一次怕什麼啊 就當回到童年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?眼鏡呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要你管!不戴又怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 你們兩個好久沒有來過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要吃昨晚鳴子做的果凍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 anaru的果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣叫我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 面碼的願望就是那個稀有口袋妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡你不要說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,anaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒事 面碼怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她託夢給我...還是怎麼說呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面碼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...口袋妖怪在...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對!那裡是LoveandBerry的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是牛王!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是牛王啊
